				<div class="elementor-widget-container">
			
					<h3 class="premium-dual-header-first-header "><span class="premium-dual-header-first-span">Debate </span><span class="premium-dual-header-second-header ">Club</span></h3> 		
				</div>
				</div>
				<div class="elementor-element elementor-element-7a020eb elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor" data-id="7a020eb" data-element_type="widget" data-widget_type="text-editor.default">
				<div class="elementor-widget-container">
							<p>Vibrance and pace setters is what PIU debate club is known for. We believe in empowering our members in skills that help them in articulation and public speaking while having fun. As members of Kenya National Debate Council, we participate in numerous debate and public speaking championships nationally. We have lots of fun travelling and competing with fellow debaters.</p>						</div>
